data.description: Introducing the Charming 156 Rearden Boulevard, Jarrell, Texas!    This delightful home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.1 baths, and formal dining area. The kitchen is a true delight, showcasing sleek stainless steel appliances, a convenient breakfast bar, and an open layout that seamlessly flows into the living area. Recessed lighting, rich espresso cabinets, and elegant granite countertops. The primary bedroom, situated at the rear of the home, offers ample space and tranquility. The primary bathroom has a double vanity, shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Uncommon in its brilliance, this single-story gem offers an exceptional floor plan that stands out. The backyard is a peaceful haven with a covered patio, perfect for unwinding. One unique feature that sets this property apart is its strategic location. Not only does it enjoy the luxury of no side neighbors, but it is also conveniently positioned directly across from the amenity centers.  Imagine stepping out and having immediate access to the pool, splash pad, and park – just a stroll away! Entertaining is a breeze in this well-appointed home, and for those times when you need extra parking, the nearby amenity center offers a convenient solution. Jarrell, TX offers the best of small-town charm with modern amenities, making this property a treasure trove of comfort and convenience. Located just off IH35, Jarrell is a vibrant and swiftly growing community. With new business developments on the rise and a strong sense of community, this town offers convenient access to State HWYs 35 and 130. Notably, the recent opening of Costco on the outskirts of Georgetown adds to the convenience of shopping.
